Action Mixer Action Graph These are the states that feed the buttons on the action mixer in game. Every action for these graphs will have a succeed and fail option.
Defining Traits of these Statemachines: - public state is NOT skipable - public state is NOT interruptible - states are public and are named Succeed and Fail - public state can have a skill parameter ( set up in the graph but not added to the state yet) - the graph can supports standing and seated postures (but will be dependant upon the posture requirments of the interaction) - Animations that populate these states will require plumbob event tags.
Always Test Your Anims With Focus and Carry !
Because there is only one posture I don't think we need the posture widget(Marion is right next to me)
